      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that but calling my doctor just to ask about a natural supplement feels like overkill... they r always so dismissive about herbs anyway. i've already started tapering down the zoloft a little bit on my own so i don't get the withdrawal stuff. if i'm already lowering my dose, wouldn't it be fine to just start the st johns wort at the same time to keep my levels steady? i just want to avoid the side effects and stay stable.",
